OL,3,CFamily prepares for first Christmas at
OL,4,Chome after 800 days in hospital
OL,6,FAfter two years fighting for his life
OL,7,Fin hospital, the toddler Gabriel is
OL,8,Fspending his first ever Christmas at
OL,9,Fhome, STV News' Amie Flett reports
OL,11,FA family who spent a record-breaking
OL,12,F800 days living at Edinburgh's Royal
OL,13,FHospital for Children and Young People
OL,14,Fare preparing to celebrate their first
OL,15,FChristmas at home together.
OL,17,FTwo-year-old Gabriel was born with a
OL,18,Frare genetic condition, and doctors
OL,19,Fthought he might only live for around
OL,20,Fthree months.
