OL,3,CFamily prepares for first Christmas at
OL,4,Chome after 800 days in hospital
OL,6,FHis parents, Teena Thomas and
OL,7,FSebastian Paul, remained by Gabriel's
OL,8,Fside throughout his treatment, staying
OL,9,Fat Ronald McDonald House while their
OL,10,Fson received round-the-clock care.
OL,12,FGabriel was discharged in August after
OL,13,Fmore than two years in the hospital
OL,14,Fand is now getting ready to spend
OL,15,FChristmas at home for the very first
OL,16,Ftime.
OL,18,F"There were times when we felt Gabriel
OL,19,Fwasn't going to make it," Teena told
OL,20,FSTV News.
