OL,6,F"He turned blue many times, it was so
OL,7,Fscary, and we cried loudly because we
OL,8,Fthought he was gone.
OL,10,F"Every time he came back, he came back
OL,11,Fwith a smile."
OL,13,FAlthough Gabriel still requires 24-
OL,14,Fhour care, his parents have been
OL,15,Ftrained to provide the support he
OL,16,Fneeds at home, alongside ongoing
OL,17,Foutreach services.
